DSS04 – Manage Continuity	Backup ada, BCP tidak terdokumentasi
DSS05 – Manage Security Services	Keamanan dasar, tanpa audit
DSS06 – Manage Business Process Controls	Kontrol proses berjalan, belum terstandar
